  "detailed_description": "It's a game of cute characters' journey to find a cool drink in the wilderness desert.<br>It is a game that can be enjoyed lightly only by keyboard operation.<br>As you move through the maze, find coins and vending machines and pick up a cool beverage can from ice.<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><br>- A maze puzzle arcade game that moves a 3D maze with 20 levels<br>- 10 selectable characters with different stats<br>- More than 30 traps and obstacles<br>- More than 20 different mobs<br>- Number of Challenges and Clear Time and Result Statistics<br>- Show directions for beginners<br>- Zoom out function for a wider view",
